00:37:12,020 --> 00:37:14,040
我在说什么?
What am I talking about?

560
00:37:15,010 --> 00:37:16,019
这是什么?
What's this?

561
00:37:16,020 --> 00:37:17,099
你的尼古丁口香糖?
Your nicotine gum?

562
00:37:18,000 --> 00:37:19,040
你不想再找那个包
You wanted to stop looking for the bag

563
00:37:19,040 --> 00:37:22,029
是因为你已经找到了
because you'd already found it.

564
00:37:22,030 --> 00:37:24,070
我知道他们在你这里  Paulo  他们在哪里?!
I know you have them, Paulo, so where are they?

565
00:37:24,070 --> 00:37:27,010
冷静一点好吗?
Calm down, okay?

566
00:37:28,000 --> 00:37:30,010
这该死的是什么?
What the hell is that?

567
00:37:32,080 --> 00:37:34,040
你疯了吗?
Are you out of your mind?

568
00:37:34,040 --> 00:37:36,049
