You remember Dr. Arzt's friend.

569
00:37:36,050 --> 00:37:38,090
它咬你了吗?
Did it bite you?

570
00:37:39,080 --> 00:37:41,049
那很疼吧?
Does it hurt?

571
00:37:41,050 --> 00:37:44,000
他告诉我为什么他们叫它"美杜莎蜘蛛"
He told me why they call it "the medusa spider."

572
00:37:44,000 --> 00:37:46,090
想知道为什么吗?
Wanna know why?

573
00:37:48,020 --> 00:37:50,050
你干了什么?
What did you do?

574
00:37:53,070 --> 00:37:57,019
因为看了美杜莎的人就会变成石头
Because one look from medusa would turn anyone to stone,

575
00:37:57,020 --> 00:38:00,049
