just like one bite from the spider will paralyze you...

576
00:38:00,050 --> 00:38:03,080
大概是8个小时
For... oh, about eight hours.

577
00:38:03,090 --> 00:38:04,090
这不会致命
It won't kill you.

578
00:38:04,090 --> 00:38:07,000
只会让你的心跳减慢
It'll just...slow your heart rate down to the point

579
00:38:07,000 --> 00:38:10,070
这个连医生也没办法...
where even a doctor would have a hard time...

580
00:38:10,080 --> 00:38:13,000
听到你的心还在跳
hearing it beat.

581
00:38:13,040 --> 00:38:15,070
你一动一不能动
You won't be able to move a muscle,

582
00:38:15,070 --> 00:38:20,059
我就能在你身上做一切肮脏的事
so I'll be able to do all sorts of nasty things to you.

583
00:38:20,060 --> 00:38:22,060
自从它咬了你之后
And since it bit you on your neck,

584
00:38:22,060 --> 00:38:26,090
效果还真是快啊
I'd say paralysis will happen fast.

585
00:38:31,040 --> 00:38:34,080
我猜钻石就在你身上
I'm guessing that you have the diamonds on you.

586
00:38:43,000 --> 00:38:45,040
也许在鞋子里?
In a shoe, maybe?

587
00:38:53,030 --> 00:38:56,050
我想我知道了
I think I know where.

588
00:39:05,010 --> 00:39:07,060
狗娘养的东西
Son of a bitch.

589
00:39:09,090 --> 00:39:11,009
我很抱歉
I'm sorry.

590
00:39:11,010 --> 00:39:14,000
你被抓到了  当然要抱歉
You're only sorry 'cause you got caught.

591
00:39:16,070 --> 00:39:20,009
