I was... afraid...

592
00:39:20,010 --> 00:39:22,030
失去你
of losing you.

593
00:39:25,000 --> 00:39:27,090
如果你找到了那些钻石...
If you found the diamonds...

594
00:39:28,010 --> 00:39:30,080
