you wouldn't need me anymore.

595
00:40:08,060 --> 00:40:11,050
该死的!
Damn it!

596
00:40:35,080 --> 00:40:38,030
你还好吗?
You okay?

597
00:40:45,010 --> 00:40:47,010
发生了什么事?
